text.tspan: Once your flights are booked and arrival time and date confirmed
we will organise the most convenient travel for you up to resort.
A private minibus for your group
A helicopter ride over the mountains
We will arrange the best option for you with minimum waiting time to get to your resort so you
can get on and start enjoying your holiday.
Recommended airports are Geneva, Lyon, Grenoble and Chambery and the nearest
train station is Bourg St Maurice.
